This product includes software derived from "The Producer V2" by slawekbiel,
published as a public Kaggle notebook:
    https://www.kaggle.com/code/slawekbiel/the-producer-v2
The orbit_lite/ package and producer_v11.py are a PyTorch port of that
design (flow-diff scorer, candidate/shortlist structure, reinforcement-risk
term) with modifications. Should the upstream notebook's license terms
differ from Apache-2.0, the upstream terms take precedence for the derived
parts.

The Indirect Wealth heuristic in agents/v117_dp15.py is inspired by the
indWealth function of the Halite 3 bot "oddshrimp" (idea only; no code was
copied).

simulator/test_golden.py uses kaggle-environments
(https://github.com/Kaggle/kaggle-environments, Apache-2.0) as the
reference implementation for equivalence testing.
